---
Title: The Sea Is Just Full of Water
By: Myokonin Saichi
Source:
  URL: "https://saltlakebuddhist.org/2013/11/05/the-sea-is-just-full-of-water-\
    asahara-saichi-poem/ [2018-02-01]"
---
The sea is just full of water;
there is the seabed that sustains it.
Saiich is just full of evil karma;
there is Amida that sustains it.
How happy I am!
